{
  "$schema_notes": [
    "Golden parity matrix for L6E-40. Canonical path: l6e/tests/fixtures/gate_parity_matrix.json",
    "  - l6e/tests/unit/test_gate_parity.py (runs l6e.gate.ConstraintGate)",
    "  - hosted-edge/tests/test_gate_parity.py (runs /v1/authorize; reads this file from sibling l6e/ in monorepo)",
    "When you add a case, BOTH tests must pass. When you change the gate",
    "decision ladder, regenerate and keep both sides in sync.",
    "",
    "Input semantics:",
    "  budget/spent/estimated_cost: decimal strings, USD",
    "  budget_mode: 'halt' | 'reroute' | 'warn'",
    "  reroute_threshold: number in [0, 1]",
    "  stage: optional string",
    "  complexity: optional 'low'|'medium'|'high' (reserved, not consulted)",
    "  stage_overrides: {stage: budget_mode}",
    "  stage_routing: {stage: 'local'|'cloud_standard'|'cloud_frontier'|'inherit'}",
    "",
    "Output semantics:",
    "  expected_action: 'allow' | 'reroute' | 'halt'",
    "  expected_reason: exact match against gate reason string",
    "  expected_tier: 'local'|'cloud_standard'|'cloud_frontier'|null (stage-routing tier hint)"
  ],
